author: Colin Stutz
title: NFL Star Tony Gonzalez Grooves to the 'Humpty Dance' on 'Lip Sync Battle': Watch
text:
Trae Patton/Spike TV Tony Gonzalez on Lip Sync Battle. 
Former NFL star Tony Gonzalez knows: The Humpty Dance is your chance to do the hump. 
On Thursday night's episode of Lip Sync Battle , the tight end and NFL Today analyst will show he knows how to get the crowd to stop what its doing as he ruins the style and the image that its used to. 
He looks funny, see, but he's just dressed up as the Digital Underground 's Shock G, performing the group's 1990 hit "The Humpty Dance." 
Gonzalez joins Lip Sync Battle to face off against fellow former NFL great Ray Lewis on Thursday at 10 p.m. PST on Spike.
